Follow the Litix tech stack: Next.js 16, React 19, TypeScript 5 strict, Tailwind CSS 4, Supabase, Trigger.dev.
Source structure: app/ (routes), features/ (domain logic), components/ (shared UI), lib/ (utilities), types/ (TypeScript types).
Run npm run lint and npm run typecheck after significant changes. Create or update tests for new logic.
Never modify supabase/migrations/ without an approved plan doc in docs/approved-plans/.
Use the self-critique checklist after implementation: bugs, edge cases, error handling, security, patterns, tests.
